title: L.I.S.A. Unveiling Spacetime with Black Hole Orbits

author: StarTalk
description:
Are we in a new space race? Neil deGrasse Tyson breaks down the original space race, from Sputnik through the dawn of NASA and Apollo 11 putting man on the moon, to our contemporary race back to the moon against China with the Artemis Program. Learn how geopolitics influences our spirit of exploration in space and more.

1:49 - The Start of NASA
